snippet.textDisplay: This is the kind of talent that people aroud the world will try to learn i think. , i assume they didnt know its possible. In the Philippines, having a good sounding voice isnt good enough to impress the people. You have to have an iconic voice.. Thats why some people came up to an idea to do both male and female voices to top the performances. its not so new to filipinos, but i believe that marcelito is the best until now. That's why he is the champion in the Philippines when we speak of singing.
